'''天主教芒加教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Mangana}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Manga}}）是[[布基納法索|布基納法索]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教瓦杜加古總教區|瓦杜加古總教區]]。

教區於1997年1月2日成立，<ref>{{cite web |title=MANGANA* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19970102_mangana.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-12-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207152253/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19970102_mangana.html |archivedate=2019-12-07 |language=la |date=1997-01-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>包括[[巴澤加省|巴澤加]]、[[宗德韋奧戈省|宗德韋奧戈]]、[[納烏里省|納烏里]]三省；2004年時有教友79,387人（佔轄區總人口15.5%）、五個堂區和十五名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 07.12.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/07/191207b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-12-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207132245/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/12/07/191207b.html |archivedate=2019-12-07 |language=en |date=2019-12-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-de|旺塞斯拉斯·孔波雷|Wenceslas Compaoré}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 28.12.2010 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/12/28/0808/01853.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-12-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207144823/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2010/12/28/0808/01853.html |archivedate=2019-12-07 |language=it |date=2010-12-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

